Title: Ghost condensates in Yang-Mills theories in nonlinear gauges
Authors: A.R. Fazio, V.E.R. Lemes, M.Picariello, M.S. Sarandy, S.P. Sorella
Comments: 9 pages, final version to appear in Mod. Phys. Lett. A
Report-no: IFUM-720-FT
\\
  Ghost condensates of dimension two are analysed in a class of nonlinear
gauges in pure Yang-Mills theories. These condensates are related to the
breaking of the SL(2,R) symmetry, present in these gauges.
